item.title: Pt. Prashant Tripathi
item.description:
Hi, I'm Pt. Prashant Tripathi
I'm a full-stack software developer specializing in Web devlopment. I like making things from scratch and learning in public. My open source projects include an Social Networking site InnovationHub, an Astrology Software, and a serach engine based upon AI/ML.
